title: Apple WWDC 2019 keynote in 13 minutes
description: At WWDC 2019, Apple announced updates headed towards the Apple family of devices, including the iPhone, iPad, Mac desktops and laptops, Apple TV, and Apple Watch. Theres also the announcement of iOS 13 and the new Mac Pro, a powerful computing device that hasnt been refreshed since 2013.
